most_popular_action.title: Most Popular Action
most_popular_action.description: The people have spoken! See the most-watched action titles now on Tubi!

283943.title: Hunt to Kill
283943.description: A border patrol agent quits and moves to the woods with his daughter, but when she is kidnapped by a band of criminals he steps back into action.

306929.title: The Devil's Brigade
306929.description: In this true WWII story, an American colonel creates the First Special Service Force from a group of misfits. A dangerous mission soon awaits.

307753.title: Kickboxer
307753.description: After a kickboxing champ is paralyzed fighting Thailand’s top fighter, his brother vows vengeance but must learn Muay Thai to fight back.

312424.title: Ronin
312424.description: A team of international mercenaries and ex-special operatives is hired to track down and steal a mysterious briefcase in this action-thriller.

314511.title: 22 Bullets
314511.description: Having been left for dead with 22 bullets in his body after being shot by a former childhood friend, a retired mobster sets out to get his revenge.

334156.title: Mad Max
334156.description: A vengeful cop and a sadistic motorcycle gang face off in a chaotic wasteland.

355108.title: The Package
355108.description: A courier for a crime lord (Steve Austin) must deliver a mysterious package while being chased by a horde of unusual gangsters.

367819.title: Titanic 2
367819.description: A century after the fateful voyage of the original, modern luxury liner Titanic II sets sail. Will this ship suffer the same fate as her namesake?

412222.title: The Kill Hole
412222.description: An Iraq War vet is forced to pursue one of his own into the Pacific Northwest wilderness to finally confront a war crime that has haunted them both.

417720.title: Tekken
417720.description: In 2039, when territories are run by corporations, a warrior rises from the streets to avenge his mother's death by entering a fighting competition.

438052.title: Centurion
438052.description: Quintus Dias, the sole survivor of a Pictish raid, marches with General Virilus' Ninth Legion, with orders to destroy the Picts and kill their leader.

460624.title: Don't Get Caught
460624.description: After stealing weed from a marijuana farm, a young man races to repay the gang of hillbilly bikers who are now holding his girlfriend hostage.

464230.title: America Has Fallen
464230.description: When an ex-Marine is linked to a bombing, he must stay one step ahead of the feds and terrorists to save the nation from a far greater catastrophe.

465867.title: Baytown Outlaws
465867.description: In the fight for her godson after being taken, a woman hires three outlaw, redneck brothers to bring him back to her.

472710.title: Lionheart
472710.description: After the murder of his brother, a tough soldier goes AWOL and enters the underground world of bare-knuckle fighting to support his family.

472714.title: Black Eagle
472714.description: When the U.S. loses a new superweapon in an air crash near Malta, a CIA agent must outrace a KGB agent to retrieve it, or his kids will pay the price.

473244.title: Falcon Rising
473244.description: After his sister is attacked by gangsters in Brazil, a dangerous man systematically stomps his way through thugs and crooks to get revenge.

477538.title: The Fearless One
477538.description: A retired fighter trades gloves for a 9-to-5 job after a tragic event but when past issues return to haunt him, he must decide which path to follow.

486566.title: Over the Top
486566.description: A truck driver attempts to reconnect with his estranged son as he road trips to Las Vegas to compete in an arm wrestling championship.

490092.title: Viking
490092.description: In the 10th century, after the death of his father, a viking prince is forced into exile, and must escape the grasp of his dangerous brother.

494842.title: Shottas
494842.description: Two young men from Jamaica climb to the top of the criminal world in Miami, with a constant presence of drugs, extortion, and deceit.

496328.title: Dolemite
496328.description: Dolemite is the role that made Rudy Ray Moore a midnight-cult-film icon as a framed pimp who fights city corruption with his all-girl Kung-Fu killers.

497642.title: Fist of Fury
497642.description: Bruce Lee stars in this iconic action film about a student who fights for the honor of the oppressed Chinese people and to avenge his master’s murder

521611.title: Tactical Force
521611.description: A SWAT captain and his team in remote training get ambushed by rival gangs searching for a rare bounty, until they turn the tables and fight back.

521967.title: Absolute Deception
521967.description: After her FBI informant husband is murdered, a journalist teams up with a federal agent in Australia’s wealthy Gold Coast to solve the crime.

523582.title: Valentine: The Dark Avenger
523582.description: A cafe waitress who dreams of acting is recruited by men she believes to be filmmakers, but who transform her into a real masked anti-crime heroine.

530056.title: Hunting Emma
530056.description: On her way home to her family farm for the holidays, young Emma sees a police officer murdered by six men who proceed to hunt down their only witness.

530166.title: Angels Fallen
530166.description: When his late wife’s prophecy comes true, a retired demon hunter returns to the dark land to rescue an angel, in whose hands rests the world’s fate.

541309.title: 2099: The Soldier Protocol
541309.description: A biotech experiment conducted by the military inside a prison gives an inmate with paralysis the ability to walk again, but at a torturous price.

543987.title: Parker
543987.description: Based on the Donald E. Westlake novels, a thief works by a code of integrity and makes it his mission to avenge all that cross him or work dirty.

548516.title: Pocket Full of Game
548516.description: A female gangster from Spanish Harlem commands respect for her loyalty, beauty and wealth before going deeper into the dangerous hustling game.

552331.title: 6 Bullets
552331.description: A former mercenary renowned for finding kidnapped children is the only hope for an MMA fighter whose daughter was abducted by child traffickers.

553874.title: Bleeding Steel
553874.description: While tracking down a deranged super-villainess, a Hong Kong detective discovers a biochemical device has been implanted into his missing daughter.

557519.title: After Earth
557519.description: Following a crash landing on Earth, a young boy and his estranged father must make an arduous journey and survive the elements to signal for help.

559203.title: Sinkhole
559203.description: After a massive sinkhole swallows an entire town, a group of teenagers must fight for their lives when their bus becomes trapped underground.

559448.title: En El Infierno (Doblado)
559448.description: Dentro de la prisión más corrupta de Europa del Este, un prisionero cumpliendo cadena perpetua se enfrenta a un alcaide en una lucha a muerte.

563905.title: Hickok
563905.description: Civil War veteran and infamous outlaw “Wild Bill” Hickok’s new life as a Kansas town marshal comes under threat by a nemesis with a deadly grudge.

565416.title: Damage
565416.description: Ex-con John Brickner joins an underground fighting community to pay for the heart transplant of the daughter of the man he killed.

572374.title: Silencer
572374.description: A former sniper with a drinking problem has to pull himself together in order to save the life of a young woman who has been taken by a cartel boss.

572512.title: DNA Bloodline
572512.description: After a conviction for involuntary manslaughter, a young man dives into his family history for a roadmap to his past in order to change his future.

572750.title: The Blackout: Invasion Earth
572750.description: A military crew discovers an outpost of survivors surrounded by corpses, from cars to hospitals, and tries to find out the cause of the mass deaths.

579292.title: Legacy of Lies
579292.description: In this pulse-pounding spy thriller, Scott Adkins stars as an ex-MI6 agent who gets dragged back into the world of espionage by a beautiful journalist.

585469.title: A Dangerous Man
585469.description: After years in special ops and wrongful imprisonment, a witness to the murder of a Chinese cop agrees to retrieve a kidnapped girl and a bag of money.

587321.title: Occupation
587321.description: When alien invaders threaten mankind, a group of random townspeople must band together and fight back against the vicious extraterrestrials.

589323.title: Superhero Movie
589323.description: In this hilarious parody of beloved blockbusters, a nerdy teenager is bitten by a radioactive dragonfly, which gives him superhuman abilities.

590016.title: Iceman
590016.description: A wild prehistoric tale, set in the Otztal Alps over 5,000 years ago, unfolds, as a Neolithic man whose settlement is attacked lives his final days.

591376.title: Rise of the Legend (Dubbed)
591376.description: An extraordinarily powerful martial artist returns to where his father was assassinated to free the people from his nemesis, a ruthless crime lord.

595031.title: Boss Moves
595031.description: When a woman coerces her husband into betraying his best friend, he becomes a sworn enemy.

599975.title: Attrition
599975.description: Axe is the leader of a special unit. He decides to retreat to the jungles of Asia, where he tries to reconcile with the life he has lived. When a desperate father asks him to save his kidnapped daughter, Axe must step in again.

604310.title: Robin-B-Hood
604310.description: Thongs and Octopus grow attached to the baby they kidnapped for their landlord, which leads to complications in handing the him over.

605932.title: Born to Raise Hell
605932.description: An American cop in Bucharest takes on Russian gun and drug traffickers and Romani gangs, who plunder, rape and kill, as he avenges his friend’s death.

607637.title: Fast Vengeance
607637.description: After his brother’s death, a man returns to his old stomping grounds, in the underworld of motorcycle racing, to deliver justice to those responsible.

610432.title: Army of One
610432.description: After drug runners murder her husband and leave her for dead on a hiking trail, a soldier sets out for revenge against the cartel responsible.

611656.title: Paydirt
611656.description: Five years after a DEA bust went wrong, a man recently released from prison teams up with his old gang to find a hidden bag of cash.

612037.title: Honor Up
612037.description: In the wake of a devastating shootout, the lieutenant for a drug syndicate kingpin fights for his honor and to save his partners in crime.

614070.title: First Lady 2: Maria's Revenge
614070.description: Revenge is a dish served cold-blooded in this hit sequel where Maria has a bounty on her head for killing the wife of the kingpin who killed her man.

620863.title: Shark Season
620863.description: Three kayakers get trapped almost four miles from shore on a remote island with a great white shark determined to keep them from getting out.

624780.title: Apocalypse of Ice
624780.description: With a pandemic already underway, a scientist with the key to human survival has to survive a devastating polar vortex that has overtaken the globe.

629330.title: Eliminators
629330.description: After a former U.S. federal agent’s home is invaded and his daughter is put in danger, he must leave the witness protection program to save her life.

631544.title: Monsters of Man
631544.description: An illegal U.S. military op goes awry when killer robots are unleashed on heroin producers in Southeast Asia and end up wiping out an entire village.

642274.title: Force of Execution
642274.description: In this explosive action thriller, two crime lords battle to rule the underworld, and a hit man with his own problems plots his rise to power.

646730.title: Fists of Fury
646730.description: A kung-fu fighter discovers the ice factory where he works is a front for the same drug trafficking ring responsible for the deaths of his relatives.

647082.title: Doomsday
647082.description: Nearly 30 years after a deadly epidemic swept through Scotland, a commander and her crew search for an antidote when the virus emerges in London.

647775.title: Broken Darkness
647775.description: Sam and his friend Troy, along with a young woman, Rose, are thrust on a journey that takes them into the darkest parts of the underground world.

654072.title: The Warrior's Way
654072.description: The world's finest warrior-assassin leaves Japan to find an old friend in the American Badlands rather than kill the infant queen of a rival clan.

657430.title: La Guerra de los Mundos: Destrucción Total (Doblado)
657430.description: Tras una invasión alienígena, la única esperanza de supervivencia que tienen una madre y su hijo radica en el descubrimiento de una verdad impensable.

660658.title: Dead Men
660658.description: A young man and his estranged brother embark on a journey to avenge their father’s death, protect the Apache tribe, and reclaim their stolen land.

668092.title: Tekken 2: Kazuya's Revenge
668092.description: Suffering from amnesia, a young man trying to uncover his identity is abducted by an underground crime ring and turned into a ruthless assassin.

668099.title: Robert the Bruce
668099.description: Injured and on the run, King Robert the Bruce is brought back to health by a widow and her nurse so that he may claim the awaited freedom of Scotland.

672479.title: Pursuit
672479.description: As he searches for his kidnapped wife, a troubled cop goes on the hunt for a ruthless hacker responsible for committing savage acts of violence.

675956.title: The Boondock Saints (Doblado)
675956.description: Dos hermanos católicos irlandeses se convierten en justicieros y acaban con el inframundo criminal de la ciudad de Boston en nombre de Dios.

676700.title: Nude Nuns With Big Guns
676700.description: Packing heat and taking no prisoners, a young nun strikes back against the men who made her life a living hell in this outrageous modern cult classic.

677117.title: Boon
677117.description: Mercenary Boon is trying to atone for his life as part of a ruthless syndicate. But when he meets a widow, he protects her by doing what he does best.

679437.title: Shark Bait
679437.description: A group of friends race stolen jet skis out to sea, ending up in a head on collision without means to get home when they realize they’re not alone in predator-infested water.

680194.title: Survive the Game
680194.description: An injured cop, his partner, and a troubled veteran join forces to outwit a drug-dealing gang that has taken over the vet’s farm as a hideout.

680467.title: Dead Zone
680467.description: To stop the collapse of humanity, an elite team of soldiers must descend on a radiation-poisoned town and perform the ultimate stealth mission using high-tech armor and weapons.

682042.title: Once Upon a Time in Venice
682042.description: Venice Beach P.I. Steve Ford is a detective who's good with the ladies, bad with the punches, and absolutely wild about his dog, Buddy.

685526.title: Accident Man (Español)
685526.description: Mike es un sicario que hace que sus asesinatos se parezcan a un accidente o a un suicidio. Cuando su ex amada es asesinada, busca a los responsables.

685745.title: Deadly Descent
685745.description: A search party in the Rockies for the lost brother of one of its members becomes a fight for survival against a creature beyond their wildest dreams.

685920.title: Brawl in Cell Block 99
685920.description: After he's fired from his mechanic gig, a hot-tempered ex-boxer enters the drug-running game which lands him in the battleground of a brutal prison.

687477.title: Justa Venganza (Doblado)
687477.description: Después de que su esposa sea brutalmente asesinada, el ejecutor del club Ben Archer emprende una guerra contra las tríadas chinas.

688267.title: MEDIDAS CORRECTIVAS
688267.description: The fragile peace of the prison is thrown into chaos with the arrival of Payback.

689752.title: Drunken Master
689752.description: After a series of incidents, a mischievous yet righteous young man is sent into a brutal training program run by a master of drunken martial arts.

693131.title: Wolf Hound
693131.description: In this thrilling WWII epic, a U.S. pilot shot down over Germany must single-handedly battle Nazi troops to thwart a doomsday plot.

693738.title: Snow Monster vs Ice Shark
693738.description: A gene research company sends a group into a mysterious snowy area on the edge of the Arctic where they get attacked by unknown giant creatures.

698132.title: The Adventures of Maid Marian
698132.description: Upon the death of King Richard the Lionheart, Maid Marian comes out of hiding to meet Robin Hood and battle the disgraced Sheriff of Nottingham.

698512.title: Hot Seat
698512.description: A reformed hacker-turned-cyber security technician finds himself in the hot seat when he realizes that he’s just armed a bomb under his chair.

700739.title: Lazarus (Español)
700739.description: Un hombre es víctima de un asesinato, pero cuando recupera la conciencia descubre que tiene poderes sobrenaturales que le permiten combatir el crimen.

701354.title: Intensive Care
701354.description: Three low-life criminals plan to rob an elderly woman's home but her caregiver turns out to be a former special ops agent with an agenda of her own.

701400.title: Detective Knight: Rogue
701400.description: While chasing bandits from Los Angeles to New York, detective James Knight crashes into his dark past, imperiling his case—and his life.

702579.title: Bring Him Back Dead
702579.description: After a heist goes wrong, a team of violent thieves gets sent to track down and eliminate the man who betrayed them and ran off with their loot.

702693.title: El Señor De Las Calles (Doblado)
702693.description: Cuando un entrenador se niega a hacer que su luchador tire una cerilla, un notorio gángster cobra la deuda matando a su luchador y secuestrando a su hija.

707345.title: Ticker
707345.description: When a madman descends on San Francisco, it's up to two men to uncover his plot and find the massive bomb he’s hidden somewhere in the city.

708103.title: Wire Room
708103.description: During surveillance, a federal agent witnesses a hit squad murder a surveillance target and soon finds himself in their crosshairs.

708254.title: Samson
708254.description: A child born with supernatural strength in 1200 BC grows up to lead his oppressed tribe with great valor against the mighty empire of his day.

712231.title: Messenger of Death
712231.description: Garret Smith travels to a sleepy Colorado town to investigate a brutal massacre and uncovers a sinister plot of greed and religious zealotry.

713456.title: Alien Sniperess
713456.description: A sniper on military leave intends to follow through on her fiancé’s dying wish until she finds herself in the middle of a hostile alien invasion.

716240.title: Highwaymen
716240.description: A deadly battle of wits and wills between a vigilante and his wife’s killer moves into overdrive and a tormented beauty unwittingly holds the key.

716411.title: Fair Game
716411.description: He's a cop on the edge, she's a woman with a dangerous secret. And when the Russian mafia sets their sights on the pair, they're both Fair Game.

723837.title: Alien Outpost
723837.description: In this pulse-pounding thriller, an elite unit of soldiers is charged with protecting a strategic outpost while under siege from an alien invasion.

100000083.title: The Double
100000083.description: A retired CIA agent and an FBI rookie are thrown together to catch a Soviet assassin, code-named Cassius, who was long-thought to be dead.

0300010409.title: Taken
0300010409.description: While dealing with a personal tragedy that shakes his world, CIA agent Bryan Mills fights to overcome the incident and exact revenge.

03325.title: Highlander
03325.description: As one of the immortals, entities who have waged a war between good and evil for centuries, a 400-year-old Scotsman fights for his destiny.

0300010081.title: Nikita
0300010081.description: Betrayed by the secret government agency that made her an assassin, the charming and deadly Nikita makes it her mission to undermine the organization.

0300010102.title: La Femme Nikita
0300010102.description: Condemned to death for a vicious crime she didn't commit, Nikita reluctantly chooses to live as an assassin for a secret government agency.
